{"title":"eclipse链接Tomcat服务器","slug":"eclipse链接Tomcat服务器","date":"2019-11-01T08:14:18.000Z","updated":"2019-11-01T09:10:06.995Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"1-打开eclipse-Myelipse\"><a href=\"#1-打开eclipse-Myelipse\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.打开eclipse/Myelipse\"></a>1.打开eclipse/Myelipse</h2><p>打开菜单栏windows/preferences 找到Server里面的Runtime Environments  添加下载好的对应版本的Tomcat服务器 点击next</p>\n<p>如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5CQQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101164615.png\" alt></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5C232111442933866.png\" alt></p>\n<p>随后选择Tomcat的所在目录和安装的Java环境</p>\n<p>如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5C232112245587963.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-导入jar包\"><a href=\"#2-导入jar包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.导入jar包\"></a>2.导入jar包</h2><p>把事先准备好的mysql jar包导入项目中WebContent/WEB-INF/lib中 (不知自行度娘)</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5CG0WK3%5B%7D8ZH%Y%5DWKK@CRFT$V.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>右击jar包 在Build pash中add它一下 项目中就会多出一个外部导入的Referenced Libraries   jar包此时就在其中静静躺着喔</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5C3R0%7B5D5SA%5B1XWB%5DG0~2UWDT.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-创建jsp文件\"><a href=\"#3-创建jsp文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.创建jsp文件\"></a>3.创建jsp文件</h2><p>此时我们已经大功告成了 现在只需在WebContent下新建JSP文件（注意 必须在WebContent此目录下创建 千万别选成META-INF或WEB-INF了 会报错）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5CQQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101165734.png\" alt=\"1572598667893\"></p>\n<p>在body中写入 Hello world 运行一下 就可以在网页中显示啦</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/11/01/eclipse链接Tomcat服务器/D:%5Chexo%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5Ceclipse%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5Tomcat%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%5CQQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720191101170501.png\" alt></p>\n<p>以后就可以用eclipse写网页了 </p>\n<p>（jsp的弊端：前后端不能实现真正分离 高耦合 低效率）</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"一giao我哩giao","path":"api/tags/一giao我哩giao.json"}]}